{"tid":2378812,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"(舊番推介)  A1P神作 皇帝聖印戰記","createTime":"2021-01-24T19:43:06.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-06T18:22:48.000Z","uid":69866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"d825d64b0931837cb3af5d4edafc1d96642f9a64","tid":2378812,"uid":69866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-24T19:43:06.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/MW3oiv5kplg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FMW3oiv5kplg&d=phsggM5TdZzYtR7qgPv%2BCK7%2FPCTF2%2B9SGuy7I2Db2XM%3D&h=53938b19\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/MW3oiv5kplg</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n紅炎之舞<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Ewo9VgTn7zk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FEwo9VgTn7zk&d=phsggM5TdZzYtR7qgPv%2BCK7%2FPCTF2%2B9SGuy7I2Db2XM%3D&h=65b255d3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Ewo9VgTn7zk</a><br />\n<br />\n最後之戰<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/AobqkxWiWpE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FAobqkxWiWpE&d=phsggM5TdZzYtR7qgPv%2BCK7%2FPCTF2%2B9SGuy7I2Db2XM%3D&h=66c7774e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/AobqkxWiWpE</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不服來戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56c261db2c7e4c09ecc8f5c77eb2245850d8dea3","tid":2378812,"uid":121580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T05:34:52.000Z","msg":"黑太子呃閪屌個段都無<br />\n講經咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38ee5930564469fa4f0d79e288447216d8df82fa","tid":2378812,"uid":304926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T06:15:43.000Z","msg":"套作品其實好三國既感覺<br />\n有人將主角比喻作劉備, 我甚至將女主當成諸葛亮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n原來真係如魚得水, 連魚水之歡都有<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n關羽係邊位都幾明顯, 仲有近身護衛趙雲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n黑太子係呂布, 劉備打呂布果一戰好有曹劉同呂布爭霸既視感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n問題係套作品好多地方好奇怪, 我覺得作者將好多橋段拼埋一齊"},{"pid":"b1bee0c456b5936eed31838a8744b73ec939e7bd","tid":2378812,"uid":230594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T06:23:22.000Z","msg":"呢套嘢動畫化前個個話佳作<br />\n動畫之後個個話劣作<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26c4f1efd483824005190e8501f5f2ca3ad07354","tid":2378812,"uid":304926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T06:25:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9738356133ed8841e833f63ce8d2d351c5f61196","tid":2378812,"uid":304926,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b1bee0c456b5936eed31838a8744b73ec939e7bd","tid":2378812,"uid":230594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T06:23:22.000Z","msg":"呢套嘢動畫化前個個話佳作<br />\n動畫之後個個話劣作<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T06:29:07.000Z","msg":"動畫化前都唔係佳作啦, 我為左避開先入為主, 先睇完小說, 然後發現, 除左第一卷描寫比較仔細外, 好多打仗謀略既地方都唔合理<br />\n其實我覺得動畫化後受眾唔同左, 以前睇開戰記既人可能接受到呢d 計謀橋段, 但動畫化之後, 多左唔同人去睇, 自然好多唔合理地方<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70020dc4a802b7e2fe2c612947183d3c5963e7b9","tid":2378812,"uid":6752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T07:07:02.000Z","msg":"最後個黑幕解話真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />..."},{"pid":"c930276b70964ecf1f607e9ae5ffeedf1b898949","tid":2378812,"uid":69866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-06T16:33:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0sC2my2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0sC2my2.jpg&h=715cd9b5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx